opical North Africa at interannual and multidecadal timescales (1998) Journal of Climate, 11, pp. 3167-3191; Zeng, N., Neelin, J.D., Lau, K.M., Tucker, C.J., Enhancement of interdecadal climate variability in the Sahel by vegetation interaction (1999) Science, 286, pp. 1537-1540","Rodríguez-Fonseca, B.; Universidad Complutense de Madrid, Departamento de Geofísica y Meteorología Facultad de Fisicas, Avda Complutense s/n, Madrid 28040, Spain; email: brfonsec@fis.ucm.es",,,,,,,,1530261X,,,,"English","Atmos. Sci. Let.",Review,Scopus,2-s2.0-79951905051
